* Serverless Compute
** What it is
***_ Managed by Databricks
***_ Runs in Databricks' Azure subscription
***_ No VMs in your subscription
** Startup
***_ 2-6 seconds
***_ Auto-scales up/down
** Available for
***_ Notebooks
***_ Jobs
***_ Pipelines
***_ SQL Warehouses
** Ideal for
***_ Exploratory analysis
***_ ETL pipelines
***_ BI workloads
***_ Latency-sensitive scenarios
** Versionless runtime
***_ Auto-upgraded by Databricks
***_ Always latest features
** Limitations
***_ No RDD APIs
***_ No R language
***_ No JAR libraries in notebooks
***_ No custom Spark configs
@endmindmap
